00:06:07.333 --> 00:06:08.559
Apa yang kamu katakan?

00:06:08.708 --> 00:06:09.739
Ya, nak.

00:06:10.606 --> 00:06:11.770
Neeti dan

00:06:12.262 --> 00:06:13.645
Gurinder

00:06:13.856 --> 00:06:15.880
telah menghancurkan rumahku.

